# InvestLogic Production Migration

## Completed
- Database: Drizzle + PostgreSQL (`pg`) via `lib/db/` and `lib/postgres.ts`
- Users & Auth: `lib/db/users.ts`, login uses DB
- Funds: `lib/db/funds.ts`, all fund APIs use DB
- Run `npm run db:seed` to create initial tenant + users

## When Replacing Mock Modules
1. Create `lib/db/<entity>.ts` with async functions
2. Update API routes to `await` and use DB
3. Update pages to `await` server data
4. Use `lib/types` for shared types (client-safe)
5. Keep `server-only` in DB modules

## RBAC
- Use `requireRBACPermission(session, PERMISSIONS.X)` in API routes
- Resolve `tenantId` from `requireTenant(session)` and filter all queries
- Roles: saas_admin, tenant_admin, fund_manager, assessor, viewer

## No Sample Data
- Remove hardcoded seeds from mock files
- If no data exists, show empty state with CTA
- Audit log should persist to `audit_log` table
